# Tsconfig Conventions

- App and package `tsconfig` files should extend the repository root `tsconfig.json`.
- Keep shared compiler defaults in the root config; keep local files focused on local overrides.

## Alias Rules

- Backend `tsconfig.json` uses the `@src/*` alias.
- Frontend `tsconfig.app.json` uses both `@src/*` and `@/*`.
- Packages may omit path aliases when they do not need them.

## Working Rules

- Preserve project references already used by the frontend root `tsconfig.json`.
- Do not duplicate base compiler settings across package configs unless there is a local override requirement.
